nodes.text: Star Wars 12 is the twelfth issue of the canon comic series Star Wars. The comic was written by Charles Soule, illustrated by Ramon Rosanas, and published by Marvel Comics on March 10, 2021.

In one panel Leia Organa is referred to as a commander rather than her correct rank of general.
In another panel Kes Dameron is referred to as a captain rather than sergeant.
